songs.title: Long Time (Intro)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
(Feel like, bitch, hello)
(Feel like, bitch, bitch)
No cap and gown, I ain't go to class
I'd rather die before I come in last (VLONE thug)

[Chorus]
I ain't felt like this in a long time (R.I.P. Fredo)
I ain't felt like this in a long time
I ain't have shit in a long time
Just to feel like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to feel like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to look like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to look like this, it took a long time, yeah

[Interlude]
Hold up, I'm tryna find—
Hold up, I'm tryna do something right now
Just leave me alone
I'd rather get caught with it than without it
Just leave me alone (Slatt, slatt)

[Verse]
Lil' black jean jacket, yeah
Got VLONE on it, yeah
Got this badass bitch, yeah
Wanna fuck me and my homie, yeah
Got this badass bitch, yeah
Tryna fuck me and my homie, yeah
Shawty gon' suck 'til the mornin', yeah
I can't wife no thot, yeah
Pass that bitch to the homie, yeah
I just fucked your thot, yeah
I ain't even pass her to homie, yeah
We might rob your homie
We might rob your home
We might rob your homie

[Interlude]
I'd rather get caught with it than without it (Slatt, thot, VLONE, slatt, slatt, slatt, what?)
Wake up and smell the motherfuckin' coffee (Yeah)
I'm 'bout to put these boys in a coffin (Yeah, we might rob your homie, VLONE thug)

[Chorus]
I ain't feel like this in a long time
I ain't feel like this in a long time
I ain't have shit in a long time
Just to feel like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to feel like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to look like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to look like this, it took a long time, yeah

[Interlude]
…Except this talk to me
You've ever been to Atlanta?
Have I been to Atlanta?
You've most definitely been to Atlanta
With who?

[Refrain]
No cap and gown, I ain't go to class
I'd rather die before I come in last

[Interlude]
Would you just send me your address, please, your address?
For here?
Woah-oh (R.I.P. Fredo)
Woah-oh
Woah-oh

[Chorus]
I ain't had shit in a long time
I ain't felt like this in a long time
I ain't felt like this in a long time
I ain't have shit in a long time
Just to feel like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to feel like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to look like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to look like this, it took a long time, yeah

[Outro]
I ain't had shit in a long time
I ain't had shit in a long time
I ain't had shit in a long time
I ain't had shit in a long time
Just to feel like this, it took a long time, yeah
Just to feel like this, it took a long time, yeah
